这是一个为您生成的HTML文件，它模拟了一张专业的科研PPT页面。

**设计思路：**
1.  **逻辑结构**：严格遵循您提供的图1（由下至上：已有项目 -> 沉淀能力 -> 支撑研究任务）。
2.  **内容提取**：
    *   **已有项目（底部）**：从图3提取“训练场”（大规模异构集群、数据）、从图2提取“DeepLink”（算子适配、编译技术）、从图4提取“Intern Bootcamp”（强化学习、系统与算法协同）。
    *   **核心能力（中部）**：将上述项目中的技术点转化为通用能力（如：国产芯片适配能力、统一编译标准、大规模调度、FP8引擎等）。
    *   **研究任务（顶部）**：对应图1的三个目标方向。
3.  **视觉风格**：采用学术/科技风格的蓝色系，使用卡片式布局，清晰展示层级关系。

您可以直接保存以下代码为 `.html` 文件并在浏览器中打开查看效果。

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>研究基础 - 算子全链路工具</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #2563eb;
            --light-blue: #eff6ff;
            --border-blue: #bfdbfe;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-gray: #475569;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .ppt-container {
            width: 1280px; /* 16:9 Standard PPT size */
            height: 720px;
            background: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 30px 50px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-blue);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .header .sub-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        /* Main Layout */
        .content-area {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Left Indicator Arrow */
        .indicator-column {
            width: 80px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            position: relative;
        }

        .arrow-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 40px;
            bottom: 40px;
            width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, var(--primary-blue) 60%, transparent 100%);
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .arrow-head {
            position: absolute;
            top: 35px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 0; 
            height: 0; 
            border-left: 8px solid transparent;
            border-right: 8px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 12px solid var(--primary-blue);
        }

        .label-text {
            background: white;
            z-index: 1;
            padding: 5px 0;
            writing-mode: vertical-rl;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }

        /* Layers Layout */
        .layers-column {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        /* Common Box Styles */
        .box {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: block;
        }

        /* TOP LAYER: Research Tasks */
        .top-layer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            height: 18%;
        }

        .task-box {
            flex: 1;
            background: var(--primary-blue);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }

        /* MIDDLE LAYER: Capabilities */
        .middle-layer {
            height: 38%;
            border: 2px dashed var(--border-blue);
            background-color: rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.5);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .capability-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .cap-column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .cap-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-blue);
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .cap-item {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-blue);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .cap-item strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        .cap-item span {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        /* BOTTOM LAYER: Existing Projects */
        .bottom-layer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            height: 28%;
        }

        .project-box {
            flex: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff, #f0f7ff);
            border: 1px solid #93c5fd;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .project-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .project-content {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .project-content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .project-content li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* Arrows between layers */
        .arrow-up-block {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 20px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .triangle-up {
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 10px solid transparent;
            border-right: 10px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 10px solid #cbd5e1;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="ppt-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>算子全链路工具汇报 - 研究基础</h1>
            <span class="sub-title">Projects & Capabilities Foundation</span>
        </div>

        <div class="content-area">
            <!-- Left Axis -->
            <div class="indicator-column">
                <div class="arrow-head"></div>
                <div class="arrow-line"></div>
                <div class="label-text" style="margin-top: 0px;">研究任务</div>
                <div class="label-text" style="margin-top: 50px; color: #64748b; font-size:14px;">支撑</div>
                <div class="label-text" style="margin-top: 50px;">能力沉淀</div>
                <div class="label-text" style="margin-top: 100px;">已有项目</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Content -->
            <div class="layers-column">

                <!-- TOP: Tasks -->
                <span class="section-label">研究任务 (Research Tasks)</span>
                <div class="top-layer">
                    <div class="task-box">
                        算子开发<br>基础设施
                    </div>
                    <div class="task-box">
                        算子编程<br>体系
                    </div>
                    <div class="task-box">
                        算子应用<br>全链路工具
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Spacer/Arrow -->
                <div class="arrow-up-block">
                    <div class="triangle-up" style="border-bottom-color: var(--border-blue);"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- MIDDLE: Capabilities -->
                <span class="section-label" style="position: absolute; top: 26%; left: 90px; background:white; padding:0 5px; z-index:2;">能力沉淀 (Core Capabilities)</span>
                <div class="middle-layer">
                    <div class="capability-grid">
                        <!-- Column 1: Hardware & Infra -->
                        <div class="cap-column">
                            <div class="cap-title">硬件与集群底座</div>
                            <div class="cap-item">
                                <strong>多芯异构适配</strong>
                                <span>适配NVIDIA、华为(910B/C)、海光(C550)、寒武纪等主流芯片</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cap-item">
                                <strong>大规模集群调度</strong>
                                <span>支持千卡/万卡级集群互联，异构算力利用率>90%</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Column 2: Software & Compilation -->
                        <div class="cap-column">
                            <div class="cap-title">编译与算子技术</div>
                            <div class="cap-item">
                                <strong>统一算子接口标准</strong>
                                <span>DIOP标准接口，屏蔽底层硬件差异</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cap-item">
                                <strong>高性能编译生成</strong>
                                <span>基于Triton的算子编译与自动优化，支持高效微调</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Column 3: App & Algo -->
                        <div class="cap-column">
                            <div class="cap-title">应用与算法协同</div>
                            <div class="cap-item">
                                <strong>系统-算法协同优化</strong>
                                <span>FP8强化学习引擎，训练成本降低10倍</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cap-item">
                                <strong>全链路开发工具链</strong>
                                <span>集成XTuner(训练)、LMDeploy(推理)及评测体系</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Spacer/Arrow -->
                <div class="arrow-up-block">
                    <div class="triangle-up" style="border-bottom-color: #cbd5e1;"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- BOTTOM: Projects -->
                <span class="section-label">已有项目支撑 (Existing Projects)</span>
                <div class="bottom-layer">
                    <!-- Project 1: Training Grounds -->
                    <div class="project-box">
                        <div class="project-title">自主可控训练场</div>
                        <div class="project-content">
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>大规模异构集群：</strong>包含华为910B (1000P)、910C (3400P)、沐曦C550等。</li>
                                <li><strong>数据资产：</strong>174PB 高质量语料存储。</li>
                                <li><strong>关键成果：</strong>实现算力设施互联混训，提供安全可信智算平台。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Project 2: DeepLink -->
                    <div class="project-box">
                        <div class="project-title">DeepLink 计算体系</div>
                        <div class="project-content">
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>核心技术：</strong>跨域异构混训、Triton算子编译、DIOP统一接口。</li>
                                <li><strong>软件栈：</strong>涵盖MaaS模型层、PaaS加速层(AI编译器)及IaaS资源层。</li>
                                <li><strong>关键成果：</strong>国产集群易用性提升，解决“卡脖子”软硬件适配问题。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Project 3: Intern Bootcamp -->
                    <div class="project-box">
                        <div class="project-title">Intern Bootcamp</div>
                        <div class="project-content">
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>场景：</strong>大规模多任务强化学习 (1000+任务)。</li>
                                <li><strong>工具链：</strong>集成XTuner训练引擎与LMDeploy推理引擎。</li>
                                <li><strong>关键成果：</strong>FP8引擎加持，系统与算法协同优化，支持复杂环境反馈。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
```

这是一个基于 **HTML + CSS** 构建的甘特图。

**设计思路：**
1.  **视觉模板（参考图1）**：采用了左侧任务标签、横向时间轴箭头、垂直虚线对齐时间点、以及关键里程碑节点（蓝色圆点代表阶段成果，红色三角形代表最终交付）的布局方式。
2.  **逻辑架构（参考图2）**：将任务分为三层，从下至上依次为“算子开发基础设施”、“产业级算子编程体系”、“算子应用全链路工具”，体现底层支撑上层的逻辑。
3.  **内容填充（参考图3）**：将图3中的表格内容（2026 Q1-Q2, Q3-Q4, 2027 Q1-Q2）转化为三个关键的时间节点：**2026.6 (阶段一)**、**2026.12 (阶段二)**、**2027.6 (阶段三/验收)**。

您可以直接保存以下代码为 `.html` 文件并在浏览器中打开。

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>项目任务与里程碑甘特图</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #f4f8fb;
            --line-color: #333;
            --blue-node: #4a90e2;
            --red-node: #d0021b;
            --task-bg-1: #e1f0fa; /* 任务3背景 */
            --task-bg-2: #e6f4ea; /* 任务2背景 */
            --task-bg-3: #fff8e1; /* 任务1背景 */
            --task-label-bg: #cde4f5;
            --dashed-line: #a0c4e8;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 1200px;
            height: 750px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: white;
            /* border: 1px solid #ddd; */
        }

        /* 标题 */
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #003366;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* 左侧任务标签列 */
        .task-sidebar {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 60px;
            width: 220px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 120px;
        }

        .task-label {
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dceefc, #f0f8ff);
            border-left: 5px solid #4a90e2;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        /* 主绘图区 */
        .chart-area {
            position: absolute;
            left: 240px;
            top: 60px;
            width: 960px;
            height: 600px;
        }

        /* 横向时间轴线 (箭头) */
        .timeline-arrow {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #000;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .timeline-arrow::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            right: -10px;
            top: -5px;
            border-left: 15px solid #000;
            border-top: 6px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 6px solid transparent;
        }

        /* 位置定义 */
        .row-3 { top: 40px; }  /* 任务3 */
        .row-2 { top: 240px; } /* 任务2 */
        .row-1 { top: 440px; } /* 任务1 */

        /* 垂直虚线 */
        .v-dash {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            bottom: -50px;
            width: 2px;
            border-left: 2px dashed var(--dashed-line);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .dash-1 { left: 25%; } /* 2026.6 */
        .dash-2 { left: 55%; } /* 2026.12 */
        .dash-3 { left: 85%; } /* 2027.6 */

        /* 节点样式 */
        .node {
            position: absolute;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: 2;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* 蓝色圆形节点 */
        .circle-node {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background-color: var(--blue-node);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px #eef6ff;
        }

        /* 红色三角形节点 */
        .triangle-node {
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 16px solid transparent;
            border-right: 16px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 26px solid var(--red-node);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%); /* 调整重心 */
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(208, 2, 27, 0.2));
        }

        /* 节点上的时间标签 */
        .date-label {
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* 内容文本框 */
        .content-text {
            position: absolute;
            top: 25px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 240px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.4;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .content-text strong {
            display: block;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }

        /* 向上支撑的虚线箭头 (SVG) */
        .support-arrows {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* 底部时间轴刻度 */
        .axis-bottom {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 50px;
            left: 240px;
            width: 960px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .axis-tick {
            position: relative;
            height: 10px;
            width: 1px;
            background-color: #333;
        }

        .axis-label {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -25px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* 图例 */
        .legend-box {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            bottom: 120px;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: white;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .legend-icon-tri {
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-left: 8px solid transparent;
            border-right: 8px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 13px solid var(--red-node);
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .legend-icon-cir {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            background-color: var(--blue-node);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-left: 2px; /* align center visually */
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>算子全链路工具项目建设进度计划</h1>

    <!-- 左侧任务栏 -->
    <div class="task-sidebar">
        <!-- 对应图2顶层，图3最后 -->
        <div class="task-label" style="background: #fff3e0; border-color: #f5a623;">
            任务三<br>算子应用全链路工具
        </div>
        <!-- 对应图2中层，图3中间 -->
        <div class="task-label" style="background: #e0f2f1; border-color: #009688;">
            任务二<br>产业级算子编程体系
        </div>
        <!-- 对应图2底层，图3最前 -->
        <div class="task-label" style="background: #e3f2fd; border-color: #2196f3;">
            任务一<br>算子开发基础设施
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 绘图区域 -->
    <div class="chart-area">

        <!-- 垂直对齐虚线 -->
        <div class="v-dash dash-1"></div>
        <div class="v-dash dash-2"></div>
        <div class="v-dash dash-3"></div>

        <!-- 支撑关系曲线 (SVG) -->
        <svg class="support-arrows">
            <defs>
                <marker id="arrowhead" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="0" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
                    <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#88badd" />
                </marker>
            </defs>
            <!-- 任务1 到 任务2 的支撑线 -->
            <path d="M 240 440 Q 280 340 320 240" stroke="#88badd" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
            <path d="M 528 440 Q 560 340 600 240" stroke="#88badd" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

